            <field name="help" type="html">
                <p class="o_view_nocontent_smiling_face">
                    <i class="fa fa-file-text-o"/> No documents yet!
                </p>
                <p>
                    <b>‚ö†Ô∏è Before creating documents, ensure you have:</b>
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>‚úì <b>Storage Containers</b> created - Go to: <i>Operations &gt; Containers</i></li>
                    <li>‚úì <b>Document Types</b> defined - Go to: <i>Configuration &gt; Master Data &gt; Document Types</i></li>
                    <li>‚úì <b>Retention Policies</b> (optional) - Go to: <i>Configuration &gt; Master Data &gt; Retention Policies</i></li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    <b>üìã To add your first document:</b>
                </p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Click the <b>New</b> button above</li>
                    <li>Enter a <b>Title</b> for the document</li>
                    <li>Select the <b>Container</b> where this document is stored</li>
                    <li>Choose a <b>Document Type</b> (e.g., "Legal", "Financial", "Medical")</li>
                    <li>Add <b>Tags</b> for better organization (optional)</li>
                    <li>Set a <b>Retention Policy</b> if applicable</li>
                    <li>Upload the actual file using the <b>Attachment</b> field</li>
                    <li>Click <b>Save</b></li>
                </ol>
                <p>
                    <b>üöÄ Key Features:</b><br/>
                ‚Ä¢ Track document lifecycle and status<br/>
                ‚Ä¢ Associate documents with containers<br/>
                ‚Ä¢ Manage retention policies and destruction dates<br/>
                ‚Ä¢ Generate compliance reports<br/><br />
                ‚Ä¢ Mobile document scanning
</p>
            </field>
